#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_color_blocks_2
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Environmental protection is the practice of safeguarding the natural world from harmful human activities and preserving ecosystems for future generations. It involves efforts to reduce pollution, conserve biodiversity, and sustainably manage natural resources such as air, water, and soil.\n"
"        <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ການປົກປັກຮັກສາສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ ແມ່ນການປະຕິບັດເພື່ອປົກປ້ອງໂລກທຳມະຊາດ ຈາກກິດຈະກຳຂອງມະນຸດທີ່ເປັ"
"ນອັນຕະລາຍ ແລະ ຮັກສາລະບົບນິເວດໄວ້ໃຫ້ຄົນຮຸ່ນຫຼັງ. ມັນລວມເຖິງຄວາມພະຍາຍາມໃນການຫຼຸດຜ່ອນມົນລະພິດ, ອະນຸ"
"ລັກຊີວະນາໆພັນ, ແລະ ຄຸ້ມຄອງຊັບພະຍາກອນທຳມະຊາດຢ່າງຍືນຍົງ ເຊັ່ນ: ອາກາດ, ນ້ຳ, ແລະ ດິນ.\n"
"        <br/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_sidegrid
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        Every step we take towards sustainability is a commitment to preserving nature's beauty and resources, for today and tomorrow."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ທຸກໆບາດກ້າວທີ່ພວກເຮົາກ້າວໄປສູ່ຄວາມຍືນຍົງ ແມ່ນການໃຫ້ຄຳໝັ້ນສັນຍາທີ່ຈະຮັກສາຄວາມສວຍງາມ ແລະ "
"ຊັບພະຍາກອນຂອງທຳມະຊາດ, ສຳລັບມື້ນີ້ ແລະ ມື້ອື່ນ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_numbers_list
msgid ""
"<br/>\n"
"        From carbon footprint reduction to renewable energy adoption and biodiversity preservation, our key milestones reflect our commitment to creating a sustainable future for all."
msgstr ""
"<br/>\n"
"        ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການຫຼຸດຜ່ອນການປ່ອຍອາຍພິດກາກບອນ ໄປຈົນເຖິງການນຳໃຊ້ພະລັງງານທົດແທນ ແລະ ການອະນຸລັກ"
"ຊີວະນາໆພັນ, ຜົນສຳເລັດທີ່ສຳຄັນຂອງພວກເຮົາໄດ້ສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນເຖິງຄວາມມຸ່ງໝັ້ນໃນການສ້າງອະນາຄົດທີ່ຍືນຍົງສຳລັບ"
"ທຸກຄົນ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_text_cover
msgid ""
"<br/>Highlight your environmental initiatives and projects with a user-"
"friendly platform that simplifies all the steps, from setup to campaign "
"management, making it easy to engage supporters and drive positive "
"change.<br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>ເນັ້ນໜັກເຖິງຂໍ້ລິເລີ່ມ ແລະ ໂຄງການດ້ານສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມຂອງທ່ານ ດ້ວຍແພລັດຟອມທີ່ໃຊ້ງານງ່າຍ ເຊິ່ງຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ທຸກ"
"ຂັ້ນຕອນງ່າຍຂຶ້ນ, ຕັ້ງແຕ່ການຕັ້ງຄ່າໄປຈົນເຖິງການຄຸ້ມຄອງແຄມເປນ, ເຮັດໃຫ້ການດຶງດູດຜູ້ສະໜັບສະໜູນ ແລະ ສ້າງກາ"
"ນປ່ຽນແປງໃນທາງບວກເປັນເລື່ອງງ່າຍ.<br/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<br/>Immerse yourself in peaceful environments that harmonize with "
"nature.<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"<br/>ດື່ມດຳໄປກັບສະພາບແວດລ້ອມທີ່ງຽບສະຫງົບ ແລະ ກົມກືນກັບທຳມະຊາດ.<br/><br/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_cover
msgid "<font style=\"font-size: 62px;\">— Life on Earth —</font>"
msgstr "<font style=\"font-size: 62px;\">— ຊີວິດເທິງໂລກ —</font>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  Eco-"
"friendly retreats"
msgstr ""
"<i class=\"fa fa-fw fa-info-circle o_not-animable\" role=\"img\"/>  ສະຖານທີ່ພັກຜ່"
"ອນທີ່ເປັນມິດຕໍ່ສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_color_blocks_2
msgid "A Call for Environmental Protection"
msgstr "ສຽງຮຽກຮ້ອງເພື່ອການປົກປັກຮັກສາສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_image_title
msgid "A Deep Dive into Conservation and Impact"
msgstr "ເຈາະເລິກເຖິງການອະນຸລັກ ແລະ ຜົນກະທົບ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_key_benefits
msgid ""
"Access specialized knowledge and innovative practices that enhance your "
"understanding and effectiveness in environmental stewardship."
msgstr ""
"ເຂົ້າເຖິງຄວາມຮູ້ສະເພາະດ້ານ ແລະ ວິທີການທີ່ມີຫົວຄິດປະດິດສ້າງ ເພື່ອເພີ່ມຄວາມເຂົ້າໃຈ ແລະ ປະສິດທິພາບຂອງທ່າ"
"ນໃນການເບິ່ງແຍງດູແລສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_freegrid
msgid "Be Part of the Change"
msgstr "ເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງການປ່ຽນແປງ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_card_offset
msgid "Be part of the change."
msgstr "ເປັນສ່ວນໜຶ່ງຂອງການປ່ຽນແປງ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_empowerment
msgid "Book a stay"
msgstr "ຈອງບ່ອນພັກ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Certification services for buildings aiming to meet green standards, "
"including energy efficiency assessments and sustainable materials "
"consulting."
msgstr ""
"ບໍລິການໃຫ້ການຮັບຮອງສຳລັບອາຄານທີ່ຕ້ອງການບັນລຸມາດຕະຖານສີຂຽວ, ລວມທັງການປະເມີນປະສິດທິພາບພະລັງງານ "
"ແລະ ການໃຫ້ຄຳປຶກສາດ້ານວັດສະດຸທີ່ຍືນຍົງ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_title
msgid "Changing the world is possible.<br/> We’ve done it before."
msgstr "ການປ່ຽນແປງໂລກແມ່ນເປັນໄປໄດ້.<br/> ພວກເຮົາເຄີຍເຮັດມາແລ້ວ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_unveil
msgid "Collaborate for a thriving planet and a sustainable future."
msgstr "ຮ່ວມມືກັນເພື່ອໂລກທີ່ສົດໃສ ແລະ ອະນາຄົດທີ່ຍືນຍົງ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_cards_grid
msgid "Committed to a Greener Future"
msgstr "ມຸ່ງໝັ້ນເພື່ອອະນາຄົດທີ່ສີຂຽວກວ່າ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_cards_grid
msgid "Community Engagement"
msgstr "ການມີສ່ວນຮ່ວມຂອງຊຸມຊົນ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_key_images
msgid "Community-driven projects for a greener future"
msgstr "ໂຄງການທີ່ຂັບເຄື່ອນໂດຍຊຸມຊົນເພື່ອອະນາຄົດທີ່ສີຂຽວກວ່າ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_pricelist_boxed
msgid ""
"Comprehensive restoration of natural habitats to support wildlife "
"conservation, including reforestation and wetland revitalization."
msgstr ""
"ການຟື້ນຟູຖິ່ນທີ່ຢູ່ອາໄສຕາມທຳມະຊາດຢ່າງຮອບດ້ານ ເພື່ອສະໜັບສະໜູນການອະນຸລັກສັດປ່າ, ລວມທັງການປູກປ່າຄືນໃໝ່ ແ"
"ລະ ການຟື້ນຟູເຂດດິນຊຸ່ມ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_carousel_intro
msgid ""
"Contribute to a healthier planet with our initiatives that promote "
"sustainability, preserve ecosystems, and combat climate change."
msgstr ""
"ປະກອບສ່ວນເຂົ້າໃນການສ້າງໂລກທີ່ດີຂຶ້ນ ດ້ວຍຂໍ້ລິເລີ່ມຂອງພວກເຮົາທີ່ສົ່ງເສີມຄວາມຍືນຍົງ, ຮັກສາລະບົບນິເວດ, ແລ"
"ະ ຕໍ່ສູ້ກັບການປ່ຽນແປງສະພາບພູມອາກາດ."

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_wavy_grid
msgid "Customized Conservation Programs"
msgstr "ແຜນງານການອະນຸລັກທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງສະເພາະ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_key_benefits
msgid "Customized Solutions"
msgstr "ທາງເລືອກທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງສະເພາະ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_images_mosaic
msgid "Discover Our Eco-Friendly Solutions"
msgstr "ຄົ້ນພົບທາງເລືອກທີ່ເປັນມິດຕໍ່ສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມຂອງພວກເຮົາ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_empowerment
msgid ""
"Discover our natural escapes   <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\" "
"role=\"img\"/>"
msgstr ""
"ຄົ້ນພົບສະຖານທີ່ພັກຜ່ອນທຳມະຊາດຂອງພວກເຮົາ   <i class=\"fa fa-long-arrow-right\" "
"role=\"img\"/>"

#. module: theme_treehouse
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_treehouse.s_features_wall
msgid "Eco-Friendly Community Programs"
msgstr "ແຜນງານຊຸມຊົນທີ່ເປັນມິດຕໍ່ສິ່ງແວດລ້ອມ"

#. module: theme_treehouse
